text: The Dollars trilogy, also known as The Man with No Name trilogy, refers to the three Spaghetti Westerns starring Clint Eastwood and directed by Sergio Leone: * A Fistful of Dollars (1964) * For a Few Dollars More (1965) * The Good, the Bad and the Ugly (1966) Category:Western (genre) movies Category:Series of movies
title: Dollars trilogy
